data.enText: a set of stairs inside a building including the posts and rails (= banisters ) that are fixed at the side

data.chText: 大理石 / 石头 / 木楼梯

tr: a way of access (upward and downward) consisting of a set of steps

value.def: A staircase is a set of stairs inside a building.

example.ex: They walked down the staircase together.
